# Living on Earth

> Living on Earth is the weekly public radio program hosted by Steve Curwood, covering environmental news, science, and policy. The archive spans 1992 to the present — over 10,000 individual segments across 1,600+ episodes.

## Key pages

- [Homepage](https://vibingon.earth/): recent episodes and segments
- [Show Archives](https://vibingon.earth/archives.html): full episode index by year (1992–present)
- [Browse by Tag](https://vibingon.earth/tags.html): all topic tags with segment counts and sparklines
- [People](https://vibingon.earth/people/curwood.html): per-host/correspondent appearance pages

## Hosts and correspondents

