## URL structure

Individual segments: `https://vibingon.earth/YYYY_MM_DD_slug.html`
Tag pages: `https://vibingon.earth/tags/tag-name.html`
Speaker pages: `https://vibingon.earth/people/slug.html`

## Content

Each segment page includes: air date, transcript, audio player (where available), topic tags, and featured speaker pills. The archive includes reruns; segments may appear under multiple dates.
